jina]]\n|\u0160portska dvorana \u010capljina\n|-bgcolor=#ccffcc\n|[[KK Igokea|Igokea]]\n|[[Lakta\u0161i]]\n|[[Lakta\u0161i Sports Hall]]\n|-\n|[[KK Kakanj|Kakanj]]\n|[[Kakanj]]\n|JU KSC Kakanj\n|-\n|[[KK Leotar|Leotar]]\n|[[Trebinje]]\n|SD Milo\u0161 Mrdi\u0107\n|-\n|[[KK Mladost Mrkonji\u0107 Grad|Mladost]]\n|[[Mrkonji\u0107 Grad]]\n|Arena Komercijalne Banke\n|-\n|[[KK Donji Vakuf|Promo]]\n|[[Donji Vakuf]]\n|\n|- bgcolor=\"lightblue\"\n|[[OKK Spars|Spars Realway]]\n|[[Sarajevo]]\n|SD Novo Sarajevo\n|- bgcolor=\"lightblue\"\n|[[OKK Sloboda Tuzla|Sloboda]]\n|[[Tuzla]]\n|SKPC Mejdan\n|- bgcolor=\"lightblue\"\n|[[HKK \u0160iroki|\u0160iroki]]\n|[[\u0160iroki Brijeg]]\n|GSD Pecara\n|-\n|[[KK Vogo\u0161\u0107a|Vogo\u0161\u0107a]]\n|[[Vogo\u0161\u0107a]]\n|SD Amel Be\u010dkovi\u0107\n|-\n|[[HKK Zrinjski Mostar|Zrinjski]]\n|[[Mostar]]\n|SD Bijeli Brijeg\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 95%;text-align:center;\"\n| style=\"background: #ccffcc;\" width=\"20\" |\n| bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" align=\"left\" |Teams that play in the [[2019\u201320 ABA League First Division|2019\u201320 Adriatic League First Division]]\n|-\n| style=\"background: lightblue;\" width=\"20\" |\n| bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" align=\"left\" |Teams that play in the [[2019\u201320 ABA League Second Division|2019\u201320 Adriatic League Second Division]]\n|}\n\n==Regular season==\n===Standings===\n{{#invoke:Sports table|main|style=WL\n|update=25 February 2020\n|source=[http://site.fibaorganizer.com/bihfed/league/34095/standings/ Basketball Federation of BiH]\n|result1=A |result2=A |result3=A |result4=A |result5=A |result6=A |result7=R |result8=R |result9=R |result10=R |result11=R |result12=R\n\n|team1 =IGO|win_IGO=17|loss_IGO=2 |gf_IGO=1618|ga_IGO=1298|name_IGO=[[KK Igokea|Igokea]]\n|team2 =SIR|win_SIR=15|loss_SIR=3 |gf_SIR=1518|ga_SIR=1313|name_SIR=[[HKK \u0160iroki|\u0160iroki]]\n|team3 =SPA|win_SPA=12|loss_SPA=6 |gf_SPA=1424|ga_SPA=1328|name_SPA=[[OKK Spars|Spars Realway]]\n|team4 =SLO|win_SLO=10|loss_SL